parts.text:
```json
{
  "application": "MMSRL",
  "software": [
    "python",
    "conda",
    "pytorch",
    "cuda",
    "cudnn",
    "gcc"
  ],
  "resource_requirements": [
    "GPU",
    "memory (80GB or more)",
    "walltime (20 hours)"
  ],
  "modules": [
    "conda",
    "pytorch",
    "cuda/10.2",
    "gcc/7.3.0",
    "cudnn/7.6-cuda-10.2"
  ],
  "commands": [
    "module purge",
    "module load conda",
    "source activate pytorch",
    "module load cuda/10.2",
    "module load gcc/7.3.0",
    "module load cudnn/7.6-cuda-10.2",
    "python -m mmsrl.train configs/ofa_old_best.py --output_val=outputs/ofa_vqa_old_max35_lr5_val.pkl --output_test=outputs/ofa_vqa_old_max35_lr5_test.pkl --save_model=models/ofa_vqa_old.bin"
  ],
  "job_submission_tool": "oarsub",
  "job_submission_options": [
    "gpu='YES'",
    "mem>80000",
    "host='nefgpu39.inria.fr'",
    "gpunum=1",
    "walltime=20:00:00",
    "t besteffort"
  ]
}
```
